{"article_id":"LzJaArbg6np6zIYg","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The case of a black man in Georgia","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"who was fatally shot in February","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"after being pursued by two armed white men","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"is gaining widespread attention among lawmakers ,","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"particularly after a graphic video of the incident was released this week .","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"`` Ahmaud Arbery was murdered","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"for being Black , ''","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"Rep Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez , D-N.Y. , said in a Thursday morning tweet .","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"`` His White assailants were allowed to roam free * for months *","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"after lynching him .","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"They faced no charges , no arrests .","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"Police had video of Ahmaud ' s murder the day","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"it happened .","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"His family deserves justice .","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"Our country deserves answers . ''","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"Ahmaud Arbery , 25 , was killed on Feb. 23","depth":5},{"id":16,"text":"when 64-year-old Gregory McMichael spotted Arbery jogging","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"and called 911","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"to report a `` black man running down the street ''","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"and said","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"he suspected","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"the man was involved in recent burglaries .","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"McMichael called his son , Travis .","depth":5},{"id":23,"text":"The pair armed themselves ,","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"and then tracked Arbery down on the road .","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"The police report says","depth":5},{"id":26,"text":"Gregory McMichael told officers","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"he and his son first tried to stop Arbery","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"by shouting ,","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"\" Stop , stop ,","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"we want to talk to you ! \"","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"The father claimed","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"that Arbery attacked his son","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"and they got into a struggle for a shotgun .","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"Police said","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"the son fired two shots .","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"Arbery 's family maintains","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"he was simply out for a jog at the time .","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"GEORGIA GRAND JURY REVIEW","depth":5},{"id":39,"text":"RECOMMENDED IN FATAL SHOOTING OF AHMAUD ARBERY , BIDEN WEIGHS IN","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"`` Justice must be blind .","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"Bring # Ahmaud Arbery 's killers to justice , ''","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"Rep. Eric Swalwell , D-Calif. , tweeted .","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"LEBRON JAMES , OTHER ATHLETES SPEAK OUT ON AHMAUD ARBERY SHOOTING","depth":4},{"id":44,"text":"The video shows a black man running at a slow pace toward a white truck","depth":6},{"id":45,"text":"that is stopped in the middle of a country road .","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"Two men are seen outside the vehicle ,","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"including one standing on the truck 's bed .","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"The black man seems to attempt to run around the truck ,","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"and","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"the moment he clears the vehicle ,","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"a shot rings out .","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"A brief struggle ensues in what looks like an effort","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"to control a shotgun ,","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"and another two shots are heard ,","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"according to the video .","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"The runner staggers away","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"and collapses .","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"The man in the truck 's bed is seen","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"holding a handgun","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"after he climbs out","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"to approach the others .","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"The public developments in the case prompted Georgia 's Republican Gov . Brian Kemp to speak out ,","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"noting","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"that the Georgia Bureau of Investigation was assisting the prosecutor","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"who has been placed on the case `` to ensure a thorough , independent investigation into the death of # AhmaudArbery .","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"GEORGIA AUTHORITIES SAYS","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"AHMAUD ARBERY CASE WILL GET FULL INVESTIGATION ;","depth":7},{"id":68,"text":"FATHER SEEKS 'JUSTICE FOR MY SON ' `` Georgians deserve answers , ''","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"Kemp said .","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"`` State law enforcement stands ready","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"to ensure justice is served . ''","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"Georgia Attorney General Chris Carr said","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"`` I am deeply concerned with the events","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"surrounding the shooting of Ahmaud Arbery , ''","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"in a brief statement","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"that was also shared by Kemp .","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"A grand jury will be reviewing the case .","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"Others","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"who have chimed","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"include Rep. Adam Schiff , D-Calif. ,","depth":7},{"id":81,"text":"who said","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"the fact","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"neither of the men","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"who were involved in the shooting","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"had been arrested","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"is , `` An all-too familiar story , ''","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"Atlanta Mayor and potential Joe Biden VP candidate Keisha Lance Bottoms ,","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"who reflected on how sad Arbury 's loss is","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"and said","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"`` May justice be served ; ''","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"and former Georgia gubernatorial candidate Stacey Abrams , also a potential Biden running mate .","depth":6},{"id":92,"text":"TREY GOWDY REACTS TO AHMAUD ARBERY CASE :","depth":6},{"id":93,"text":"'WHY DID IT TAKE THE VIDEO ' TO RECOMMEND GRAND JURY REVIEW ?","depth":6},{"id":94,"text":"`` I believe","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"that there should be [ an ] immediate investigation of charges , ''","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"Abrams said on MSNBC Wednesday .","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"`` It looks like murder .","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"It looks like vigilante behavior","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"that should be charged and criminalized .","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"And it looks like the Arbery family has been dealt a very sore hand of injustice . ''","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"Former Rep. Trey Gowdy , R-S.C. ,","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"who is a former prosecutor ,","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"said","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"he was surprised","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"it took the video being released","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"to get prosecutors to ask for a grand jury review .","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"`` I guess","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"my first question would be , why did it take the video","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"[ becoming public ] ? ''","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"Gowdy asked Fox News ' Dana Perino on `` The Daily Briefing . '","depth":8},{"id":111,"text":"' `` If you have someone","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"who is jogging ,","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"who is unarmed ,","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"who is shot and killed by officers","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"who are n't officers","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"-- they are n't even law enforcement officers --","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"why did they take video ? ''","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"The video even prompted Biden himself to weigh in earlier in the week .","depth":7},{"id":119,"text":"`` The video is clear :","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"Ahmaud Arbery was killed in cold blood , ''","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"he tweeted .","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"`` My heart goes out to his family ,","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"who deserve justice","depth":11},{"id":124,"text":"and deserve it now .","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"It is time for a swift , full , and transparent investigation into his murder . ''","depth":9},{"id":126,"text":"Tom Durden , the prosecutor","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"who was put on the Arbery case","depth":12},{"id":128,"text":"after the previous two resigned due to previous professional ties with the older McMichael ,","depth":12},{"id":129,"text":"called for the case to be reviewed by a grand jury ,","depth":10},{"id":130,"text":"though he did not make clear","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"what charges the grand jury should consider .","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"But due to Georgia 's orders","depth":12},{"id":133,"text":"to prevent the spread of the coronavirus ,","depth":12},{"id":134,"text":"a grand jury would not be able to convene until at least June 13 ,","depth":11},{"id":135,"text":"according to Fox 5 Atlanta ,","depth":10},{"id":136,"text":"meaning there is a chance","depth":10},{"id":137,"text":"the McMichaels will remain free until at least then .","depth":10},{"id":138,"text":"Some have called for the police to detain the McMichaels ,","depth":10},{"id":139,"text":"who have not been charged ,","depth":10},{"id":140,"text":"in the meantime .","depth":9},{"id":141,"text":"`` That is disturbing","depth":11},{"id":142,"text":"and that needs to be resolved in detention until trial , ''","depth":11},{"id":143,"text":"lawyer John Phillips told News4Jax of Jacksonville , Fla.","depth":10},{"id":144,"text":"`` That ' s what it smells like is up to me","depth":10},{"id":145,"text":"is that there is just an intent","depth":12},{"id":146,"text":"not to prosecute these guys","depth":12},{"id":147,"text":"and they need to be prosecuted","depth":12},{"id":148,"text":"whether that ' s by a grand jury indictment or filing charges right now under Georgia law","depth":13},{"id":149,"text":"and get in the indictment later for the higher charges","depth":14},{"id":150,"text":"they have those options available to them . ''","depth":14}],"relations":[{"parent":301,"left":188,"right":300,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":188,"left":165,"right":187,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":165,"left":155,"right":164,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":155,"left":153,"right":154,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":153,"left":0,"right":152,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":152,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":154,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":164,"left":160,"right":163,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":160,"left":157,"right":159,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":157,"left":156,"right":7,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":156,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":159,"left":158,"right":10,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":158,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":163,"left":161,"right":162,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":161,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":162,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":187,"left":174,"right":186,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":174,"left":171,"right":173,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":171,"left":15,"right":170,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":170,"left":16,"right":169,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":169,"left":166,"right":168,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":166,"left":17,"right":18,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":168,"left":19,"right":167,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":167,"lef